{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"bg_adv_23051.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":200101,"motion":0,"pos":1,"soulGem":0}],"item":[{"anchor":"skip","path":"resource/scenario/img/scene0/calender_day03_s.png","posX":-4,"posY":-50,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"messageFront"}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"bgm":"bgm01_anime03","chara":[{"id":200101}],"nameAvCenter":"Madoka","textAvCenter":"[fontSize:20]Good morning.","textAvColor":"textMadoka","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":200101}],"textAvClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":810600,"motion":100,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":200401,"motion":1,"pos":0,"soulGem":0}],"nameAvRight":"Hitomi","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Good morning, Madoka."},{"chara":[{"id":200401}],"nameAvLeft":"Sayaka","textAvColor":"textSayaka","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Morning, Madoka."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"id":200401,"pos":2}],"textAvClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":200401},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":200101,"motion":0,"pos":0,"soulGem":0}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Aren't you a little late today?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":200101,"motion":300}],"nameAvLeft":"Madoka","textAvColor":"textMadoka","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Ah, um... I just went to bed@a little late yesterday."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":810600,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameAvRight":"Hitomi","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Oh? That's rather rare@for you, Madoka."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":200401,"motion":201,"pos":2,"soulGem":0}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvColor":"textSayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]I bet you were so worried about the@math exam that you couldn't sleep, right?"},{"chara":[{"id":200101,"motion":0}],"nameAvLeft":"Madoka","textAvColor":"textMadoka","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]No, umm...@It's not that."},{"chara":[{"id":200101}],"nameAvLeft":"Madoka","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]I was just doing a bit of thinking..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":810600,"motion":300,"pos":2}],"nameAvRight":"Hitomi","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Love troubles, perhaps?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":200101,"motion":201}],"nameAvLeft":"Madoka","textAvColor":"textMadoka","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]As if! Jeez."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"id":200101,"motion":1}],"nameAvLeft":"Madoka","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Say, um...if you could wish for anything,@just once..."},{"chara":[{"id":200101}],"nameAvLeft":"Madoka","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]What would you two wish for?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":200401,"motion":100,"pos":2,"soulGem":0}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvColor":"textSayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Huh? Is that what you were up all night@fantasizing about?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"id":200101}],"nameAvLeft":"Madoka","textAvColor":"textMadoka","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Well, um...[chara:200101:lipSynch_0][wait:0.8][chara:200101:eyeClose_1][chara:200101:lipSynch_1]yeah."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":200401}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvColor":"textSayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20][chara:200401:effect_emotion_joy_0][se:7222_happy]Ahahaha!@That's so YOU, Madoka!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":810600,"motion":1,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"id":200101}],"nameAvRight":"Hitomi","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Well, if we really could have@a single wish granted..."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":810600}],"nameAvRight":"Hitomi","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]I would wish for health."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp3.json","id":200101,"motion":101,"pos":0}],"nameAvLeft":"Madoka","textAvColor":"textMadoka","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Health? Not something like immortality?"},{"chara":[{"id":810600,"motion":100}],"nameAvRight":"Hitomi","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Even if you could wish for anything,@there's no point if your health fails you."},{"chara":[{"id":810600}],"nameAvRight":"Hitomi","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]As long as your body is healthy, you can@just fulfill your desires on your own."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_041.exp3.json","id":200101}],"nameAvLeft":"Madoka","textAvColor":"textMadoka","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Ahahaha...@That's so you, Hitomi."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":200101,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameAvLeft":"Madoka","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]What about you, Sayaka?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":200401,"motion":0,"pos":2,"soulGem":0}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvColor":"textSayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Uhh, me?"},{"chara":[{"id":200401,"motion":300}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]I...[chara:200401:lipSynch_0][wait:1.2][chara:200401:lipSynch_1]don't think I've got one."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_051.exp3.json","id":200101}],"nameAvLeft":"Madoka","textAvColor":"textMadoka","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]You don't...?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":200401}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvColor":"textSayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]It's not like I have gripes about@my current life."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":200401,"motion":1}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Sure, there might be tons of stuff@I want, but..."},{"chara":[{"id":200401}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Even if I was loaded with money,@there'd just be no end to it."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_041.exp3.json","id":200401}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]So I think having burgers with you two@is just about enough for me."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":810600,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameAvLeft":"Hitomi","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Oh, Sayaka..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":200101,"motion":1,"pos":0,"soulGem":0}],"nameAvLeft":"Madoka","textAvColor":"textMadoka","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Surely you want your CDs even more@than that."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":200401,"motion":0}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvColor":"textSayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Well...[chara:200401:lipSynch_0][wait:0.8][chara:200401:cheek_0][chara:200401:face_mtn_ex_041.exp3.json:motion_100][chara:200401:lipSynch_1]yeah, ahaha.@You might be right about that, but..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":200401}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]It's like what Hitomi said."},{"chara":[{"id":200401,"motion":201}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]There's no point if you can't get it@with your own hands."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":200101,"motion":300}],"nameAvLeft":"Madoka","textAvColor":"textMadoka","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]I see...@Yeah, you're right."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":200401,"motion":0}],"nameAvRight":"Sayaka","textAvColor":"textSayaka","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Also, what's going on?@This wish stuff came out of nowhere."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":200101,"motion":0}],"nameAvLeft":"Madoka","textAvColor":"textMadoka","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]It's okay, it's nothing."},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}
